job.title: CRPF Assistant Commandant Recruitment 2021  Apply online for 25 Vacancies in India
job.body:
Total vacancies:25

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Assistant Commandant

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Civil Engineers has been published by Central Reserve Police Force for Assistant Commandant vacancies in India. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Assistant Commandant from 01-06-2021, and till 29-07-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for Unreserved/EWS/OBC (Male) category candidates is only Rs.400/- 
  • The application fee for SC/ ST/ Female Candidates category candidates is only Nil

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for an Assistant Commandant in CRPF, your Bachelors Degree (Civil Engineering) must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 29-07-2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

CRPF Assistant Commandant Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for CRPF Assistant Commandant Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Assistant Commandant Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of CRPF and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by CRPF
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
